{"by":"tikimcfee","id":47767538,"parent":47765746,"text":"Hello folks! Thanks for taking the time to read &lt;3<p>Project name: glpyh3d-js<p>Project description<p>- High performance, high quality text rendering in true 3d space<p>- Original implementation in Swift + Metal, ported to raw JS and Three.js usage<p>- Totally agent friendly with a local loopback service to remotely control the application state, move cameras, update glyph collections live, with the first few steps of &#x27;watching an agent move around files&#x27; live and in testing; works off of a generic command server and exposed internals for true hackery shenanigans.<p>What do you hope to build this month?<p>- I have been working on a proof of concept IDE using the rendering backend. It&#x27;s live and you can play with it:<p>- <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ivanlugo.dev&#x2F;app&#x2F;ide.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ivanlugo.dev&#x2F;app&#x2F;ide.html</a><p>- OR, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ivanlugo.dev&#x2F;ide&#x2F;&lt;github_owner&gt;&#x2F;&lt;repo_name&gt;, e.g., <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ivanlugo.dev&#x2F;ide&#x2F;tikimcfee&#x2F;glyph3d-js\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ivanlugo.dev&#x2F;ide&#x2F;tikimcfee&#x2F;glyph3d-js</a><p>What kind of skills do you need?<p>- Folks that are interested in 3D layout, visiospatial relationships of files, text, and navigating large corpuses of data.<p>- Anyone that&#x27;s able to slog through weird 3D paradigms and graphics rendering libraries to turn typical 2D canvas rendering and text editing into a fully realized, high-performance 3D arena.<p>How to contact you?<p>- Email me at ivan.lugo.dev@pm.me, star the repo and leave an issue &#x2F; discussion, or stalk me through the innermanetz and find something I forgot was public.<p>- It&#x27;s OSS, through and through, and the repo itself is both the code, the IDE, and my personal page. I&#x27;ll get it split eventually, but I&#x27;ll do that when I have folks helping that don&#x27;t need all that cruft alongside ;)<p>Linkees:\n- <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ivanlugo.dev\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ivanlugo.dev</a>\n- <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;tikimcfee\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;tikimcfee</a>\n- <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;tikimcfee&#x2F;glyph3d\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;tikimcfee&#x2F;glyph3d</a>\n- <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;tikimcfee&#x2F;glyph3d-js\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;tikimcfee&#x2F;glyph3d-js</a>","time":1776183105,"type":"comment"}